<item>
            <title>[HIVE-14751] Add support for date truncation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-14751</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add support for &lt;tt&gt;floor (&amp;lt;time&amp;gt; to &amp;lt;timeunit&amp;gt;)&lt;/tt&gt;, which is equivalent to &lt;tt&gt;date_trunc(&amp;lt;timeunit&amp;gt;, &amp;lt;time&amp;gt;)&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.postgresql.org/docs/9.1/static/functions-datetime.html#FUNCTIONS-DATETIME-TRUNC&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://www.postgresql.org/docs/9.1/static/functions-datetime.html#FUNCTIONS-DATETIME-TRUNC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
